content: I don't have access to the personal experiences and decisions of the elected. however, collaborations can influence musicians to make changes to their sound or style. while it's up to the artist to decide how much they want to let collaborations impact their artistic direction, collaborators can bring new influences, sounds and ideas to the table that can influence the artist and shape their sound. it's possible that collaborations have influenced the elected's sound and style in one way or another, but the extent and nature of these influences can only be conveyed by the band members themselves.
